   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Tuffy doesn't even show on IE8, which means that the font serving CSS doesn't
care for older IEs. Win XP with Firefox looks exactly like Win 7. I would mark
this as resolved, worksforme/notabug/wontfix, if you are not willing to switch
from Tuffy.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
